WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.989
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.989 --> 00:00:04.103
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:04.103 --> 00:00:05.960
Well, we're here again.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:08.343
We're going to do another prayer video for you.

00:00:08.343 --> 00:00:14.550
It's Brandon and Diana, the dynamic duo.

00:00:20.865 --> 00:00:21.575
We want to tell you a quick testimony.

00:00:21.575 --> 00:00:27.111
Braden was a part of it.

00:00:27.111 --> 00:00:43.822
Diana was pregnant with our third child and we were just getting off work and headed home.

00:00:43.822 --> 00:00:47.413
Our truck—we had an old truck that the gas gauge was broken on.

00:00:47.413 --> 00:01:08.262
Whenever you were out of gas, you were out of gas; you just didn't know because the gas gauge didn't work.

00:01:14.604 --> 00:01:32.207
I would always try to keep it full, but when you're running low on money, you can't always keep a big truck like that full of gas.

00:01:32.895 --> 00:01:56.622
I didn't realize how low we were, so we were just driving down the road, going down I-35 in Oklahoma, going down I-35, and all of a sudden the engine just turned off.

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:01.412
It started sputtering and it just turned off.

00:02:01.412 --> 00:02:04.380
I thought, 'Oh no.

00:02:04.380 --> 00:02:12.120
' Diana was sitting there pregnant, the two kids were in there, and it was hot.

00:02:14.836 --> 00:02:19.1000
The air conditioner didn't work and it was probably around 100 degrees.

00:02:21.099 --> 00:02:23.476
It was very, very hot.

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:43.879
I started praying in the spirit, grabbed the wheel, and was just like, 'God have mercy,' because we were on the highway in the middle of nowhere.

00:02:43.879 --> 00:03:01.440
It seemed like people were driving fast and I thought I'd have to get out and walk to the gas station several miles away.

00:03:06.316 --> 00:03:20.102
I told Diana, 'I'm going to go,' even though we were far out in the country with no exits near.

00:03:20.102 --> 00:03:32.855
We were going through hills and flat plains and it was so hot.

00:03:42.004 --> 00:03:57.805
The kids were in the back seat, we were in the front, and when the car just turns off, fear hits you.

00:04:16.151 --> 00:04:25.644
I had my beautiful wife and two kids, she's pregnant, there's no air, it's 100 degrees, and I have to roll down these windows and walk for help.

00:04:25.644 --> 00:04:39.554
So I pulled off on the shoulder and all of a sudden I just started praying in the spirit.

00:04:40.423 --> 00:04:46.977
I told her, 'You need to pray in the spirit.

00:04:46.977 --> 00:04:51.549
Help me, let's pray.

00:04:51.549 --> 00:05:05.919
' Even Braden, little as he was, was praying in the back seat.

00:05:05.919 --> 00:05:27.240
Megan was sitting in the back seat fussing already because she was already really overwhelmed with autism, and it was rough and hot.

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:41.933
Braden started praying, we all started praying, and all of a sudden we felt like we got hit from behind.

00:05:43.827 --> 00:05:45.293
It shook the whole truck.

00:05:56.457 --> 00:05:56.742
It was a boom.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:06:12.097
I jerked, looked in my rearview mirror, and looked behind us thinking somebody just rear-ended us.

00:06:20.805 --> 00:06:21.260
It jolted us so much.

00:06:25.039 --> 00:06:41.396
The Lord allowed me at that time to see in the spirit, and I saw this massive angel with huge wings, like Angels in the Outfield.

00:06:41.396 --> 00:06:43.460
A massive wingspan.

00:06:43.460 --> 00:06:56.182
He grabbed ahold of that tailgate and smiled at me with these huge chubby cheeks.

00:06:56.182 --> 00:07:05.869
He grinned from ear to ear and started pushing our truck down the highway.

00:07:05.869 --> 00:07:12.800
It was all supernatural because the truck was off.

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:37.160
How I had power steering or any kind of control over an off truck is still a miracle to me.

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:56.719
When it first happened, I thought the car was doing some kind of sputter because I felt the jerk, but then I felt us accelerating again.

00:07:56.719 --> 00:08:09.085
That's when Brandon saw what he saw and I was like, 'Praise God!

00:08:09.085 --> 00:08:16.695
' Well, we started picking up speed.

00:08:16.695 --> 00:08:18.159
It accelerated.

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:32.004
We went from zero to 70 miles per hour just like that.

00:08:32.004 --> 00:08:44.570
I had to turn my blinker on to re-enter the highway because we were going with such momentum.

00:08:45.780 --> 00:08:55.600
It wasn't slow; we started passing people in the left-hand lane.

00:09:11.173 --> 00:09:15.340
We were going so fast with that angel pushing us to the gas station that we started passing people in the fast lane.

00:09:18.675 --> 00:09:29.660
I looked and said, 'Hey, are you putting your foot on the gas?

00:09:29.660 --> 00:09:42.800
' He lifted his foot and said, 'I'm not pushing on it at all.

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:56.263
' You could feel the car accelerating and the breeze blowing into the truck from the speed.

00:09:56.263 --> 00:10:08.690
I had my hazard lights on because I'm thinking people need to know.

00:10:13.390 --> 00:10:18.575
We were laughing and rejoicing in shock.

00:10:19.669 --> 00:10:22.200
It was very surreal.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:37.109
The angel was grabbing ahold of the tailgate, smiling from ear to ear, and I could feel it.

00:10:37.109 --> 00:10:47.696
It's one of those moments where you go, 'Am I dreaming?

00:10:47.696 --> 00:10:51.100
Is this really happening?

00:10:51.100 --> 00:11:03.634
' Braden is praying in the spirit and I'm saying, 'Pray louder, pray louder!

00:11:03.634 --> 00:11:17.794
' He's yelling in tongues, Diana's praying in tongues, and we're going faster and faster.

00:11:17.794 --> 00:11:34.314
We weren't breaking the law, but we went from nothing to probably 70 miles per hour passing people.

00:11:34.314 --> 00:11:50.600
We went two and a half miles all the way down, exited the highway, and came to a stoplight.

00:11:50.600 --> 00:12:11.610
He stops the truck at the red light, we turn right, and he pushes the truck again through the stoplight.

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:35.056
We went down another couple blocks, turned right again, and he pushed us all the way until we were in front of the gas station pump.

00:12:35.056 --> 00:12:50.227
He yanked the tailgate and stopped the truck right in front of the gas pump.

00:12:50.227 --> 00:13:07.851
Other people were pumping gas and we started screaming at the top of our lungs, 'Glory to God!

00:13:07.851 --> 00:13:23.668
' All the people at the gas pumps were looking at us like, 'What's going on?

00:13:23.668 --> 00:13:29.258
' because our windows were down.

00:13:45.199 --> 00:13:45.519
We were in such shock and awe at what God did.

00:13:45.519 --> 00:14:06.776
When we got to the gas station, we were just yelling, hooting, and hollering, celebrating what Jesus just did for us.

00:14:06.776 --> 00:14:18.615
Getting us off the highway, passing cars, getting us through the stoplights...

00:14:28.149 --> 00:14:28.334
I still look back and go, 'But God.

00:14:28.334 --> 00:14:35.699
' When we got to the pump, the angel disappeared.

00:14:36.495 --> 00:14:55.908
I put gas in the truck and everybody around us just looked at us like, 'Why are they screaming?

00:14:55.908 --> 00:15:02.120
' but we were just rejoicing.

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:08.168
Braden will never forget it.

00:15:08.168 --> 00:15:10.191
It's amazing.

00:15:10.191 --> 00:15:32.550
When something like that happens and you're believing for a miracle, you think, 'Lord, how's it going to come through?

00:15:32.550 --> 00:15:41.349
' But God, in the least expected way.

00:15:41.349 --> 00:15:47.130
We weren't expecting that at all.

00:15:47.130 --> 00:15:51.167
It was just shock and awe.

00:16:03.968 --> 00:16:06.828
I remember passing a person in a little white car and thinking, 'They don't even know.

00:16:06.828 --> 00:16:23.360
' And how I had control over the power steering—it wasn't in neutral, it was still in drive.

00:16:23.360 --> 00:16:28.684
There was no engine sound.

00:16:29.534 --> 00:16:40.062
You still try to calculate it and say, 'How did that happen?

00:16:40.062 --> 00:16:44.663
' But God.

00:16:44.663 --> 00:17:01.159
When you try to wrap your mind around the supernatural, you can't; the natural man perceiveth not the things of the Lord.

00:17:01.159 --> 00:17:11.029
Even whenever He's doing something so big and so mighty, you're trying to put your intellect to the supernatural and figure out how He did that.

00:17:19.333 --> 00:17:19.644
I know the angels are real.

00:17:23.653 --> 00:17:41.333
I believe with all my heart what He said in Psalm 91: He sent His angels to protect us.

00:17:54.294 --> 00:17:54.585
But when you actually have an experience that defies the laws of everything...

00:17:54.585 --> 00:18:03.319
cars don't go down the road fast with the engine off.

00:18:04.980 --> 00:18:25.330
You go back and try to make sense of it in the natural, kind of like when she was not having any pain in birth.

00:18:25.330 --> 00:18:36.655
We believe for big, but when big shows up, it shakes you.

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:54.159
I thought about whenever the children of Israel saw the sea open up, or the cloud by day and the fire by night.

00:18:54.159 --> 00:19:10.120
Whenever we have some kind of supernatural manifestation take place, it shakes you.

00:19:10.120 --> 00:19:48.059
I don't know if any of you have had some kind of demonstration of the glory in your household; you probably can testify to it too, because I know He's not just done it for us.

00:19:48.059 --> 00:20:01.524
People all over the world have things happen for them too.

00:20:03.176 --> 00:20:15.440
I just thought I would tell you all to believe God again for big.

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:36.885
Don't settle for second best; believe God for the best, exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:20:36.885 --> 00:20:44.480
That was just one testimony of many we've had.

00:20:44.480 --> 00:20:52.453
Paisley praying for the dead dog, visitations, healings...

00:20:52.453 --> 00:20:57.380
but that one stands out.

00:21:03.930 --> 00:21:08.146
When you're having a hard day and you're out of gas, He cares.

00:21:10.262 --> 00:21:14.777
I know that if you believe, it will happen.

00:21:19.195 --> 00:21:29.120
He is not a respecter of persons, but He is a respecter of faith and a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:21:34.635 --> 00:21:37.980
I continue every day to put God first and we practice His presence.

00:21:55.240 --> 00:21:55.560
I talk to the Father like I'm talking to Diana right now.

00:21:55.560 --> 00:22:06.029
We do not act like God is 'thee' and 'thou,' super hyperspiritual.

00:22:06.029 --> 00:22:12.509
I talk to Him like He's my friend.

00:22:12.509 --> 00:22:22.484
I don't talk to Him as, 'Oh thou lovest me,' the way people act so religious.

00:22:34.933 --> 00:22:35.186
When you get real with God, God will get real with you.

00:22:51.497 --> 00:22:51.731
God spoke to me one time and said, 'Diana, I'm not an algorithm to be figured out.

00:22:51.731 --> 00:23:00.905
' So stop putting God in a box.

00:23:00.905 --> 00:23:13.337
When we expect Him to move, we don't control how He does it.

00:23:13.568 --> 00:23:31.491
You can't do what you did before to get Him to do it again.

00:23:31.491 --> 00:23:42.680
You cannot box God in thinking you can control Him.

00:24:00.180 --> 00:24:00.472
A lot of people try to do that.

00:24:00.472 --> 00:24:43.480
They camp at an experience they had when they were 17, thinking they can get Him to do the same exact thing by doing exactly what they did—singing this song, fasting for 24 hours, taking communion.

00:24:43.480 --> 00:24:45.820
It's foolish.

00:24:45.820 --> 00:25:01.229
I've tried to do it, but it's in times when you least expect it that He shows up.

00:25:01.229 --> 00:25:16.097
When He shows up, it's because He has a word; He's wanting to say something.

00:25:16.097 --> 00:25:28.720
It's like what Roberts said: God does not speak just to hear Himself talk.

00:25:35.947 --> 00:25:36.720
He speaks to make real things happen in a real world.

00:25:36.720 --> 00:25:38.725
I love that.

00:25:38.725 --> 00:25:45.742
Oral Roberts was amazing; he walked with the Lord.

00:25:45.742 --> 00:26:03.040
A lot of people say, 'Brandon, how did you have these visitations and these things in the spirit realm?

00:26:03.040 --> 00:26:19.070
' I can honestly tell you it's just by a daily relationship.

00:26:19.070 --> 00:26:31.954
Every day, the mundane; you seek Him on a day-to-day basis and build relationship like building blocks.

00:26:31.954 --> 00:26:36.290
In consistency lies the key.

00:26:36.290 --> 00:26:55.040
It's like when your husband brings home roses; it's not about what you did, it's just the relationship.

00:27:01.399 --> 00:27:02.525
It takes years to the point where you expect it.

00:27:06.489 --> 00:27:10.604
I expect Him to move in my life.

00:27:18.900 --> 00:27:22.280
I go, 'Hey Lord, how are you doing today?

00:27:22.280 --> 00:27:28.640
' It's a dialogue, not a monologue.

00:27:34.309 --> 00:27:37.488
Don't always anticipate Him to say the same thing.

00:27:37.488 --> 00:27:42.548
I'm always looking for a new answer.

00:27:42.548 --> 00:27:59.519
When you start dishonoring Him as cookie-cutter, you're not going to have a relationship with Him.

00:27:59.519 --> 00:28:15.260
We were praying about some investments and He told my wife, 'Tell him I have millions of ways to get you the money.

00:28:15.260 --> 00:28:50.650
' When I was talking to Him about finances, He said, 'Diana, there's not really anything you can mess up in that area because I've got millions and billions of ways to get you the money you need for your family.

00:28:50.650 --> 00:29:00.920
' I was limiting Him to one certain area, but God has infinite avenues.

00:29:00.920 --> 00:29:07.480
When you think it has to be through a certain avenue, you're limiting God.

00:29:13.089 --> 00:29:16.880
We pray about things all the time.

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:34.111
If you miss the boat, all's not lost; He'll send a new one.

00:29:34.111 --> 00:29:46.834
Take the care out of your prayer and lay it at His feet.

00:29:46.834 --> 00:30:07.216
Philippians 4:6-8 says: 'Be careful for nothing; but in everything by prayer and supplication with thanksgiving let your requests be made known unto God.

00:30:07.216 --> 00:30:23.479
' There is a key: being thankful, not full of care concerning your finances, health, or marriage.

00:30:23.479 --> 00:30:31.159
Let your requests be made known to God.

00:30:32.142 --> 00:30:38.269
I'm not going to worry about tomorrow.

00:30:38.269 --> 00:30:56.537
Whenever He's telling you to do something, you need to be obedient.

00:31:02.434 --> 00:31:09.160
The willing and the obedient eat the good of the land.

00:31:09.160 --> 00:31:17.633
Following His voice on a day-to-day basis.

00:31:23.559 --> 00:31:32.340
The footsteps of the righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:31:32.340 --> 00:31:51.695
As long as you're keeping your eyes upon Him, you're not big enough to mess your life up.

00:31:51.695 --> 00:32:00.880
You're not big enough to derail your life.

00:32:00.880 --> 00:32:13.680
What the devil meant for bad, God said He'll turn it around for good.

00:32:13.680 --> 00:32:31.821
No matter how much you think you've messed up, He knows how big the mistake is.

00:32:31.821 --> 00:32:34.355
But God.

00:32:34.355 --> 00:32:52.068
What the devil meant for bad, God said He'll turn it around for good in your favor.

00:32:55.264 --> 00:33:04.213
I just want to encourage you all today: believe God for big.

00:33:04.213 --> 00:33:20.296
If you stumble and fall, pick yourself back up and keep going.

00:33:20.296 --> 00:33:33.679
God's got a million and one ways to bring you out of the hole you're in.

00:33:33.679 --> 00:33:44.286
He'll come through in ways you can't even imagine.

00:33:44.286 --> 00:33:55.149
He can invent a new way that no one's ever seen or heard.

00:34:13.609 --> 00:34:14.040
I hope that blessed you all.

00:34:14.040 --> 00:34:23.229
Your best days are right in front of you.

00:34:23.229 --> 00:34:37.754
His mercies are new every morning and great is His faithfulness.

00:34:48.959 --> 00:34:49.279
The best is yet to come.

00:34:49.279 --> 00:35:06.800
There are great days for the body of Christ and it's not all doom and gloom.

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:10.107
Regardless, we win.

00:35:10.107 --> 00:35:37.384
He has overcome the world, and we have overcome the world by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:35:37.384 --> 00:35:56.484
No matter how dark it may get, God has provided a way out of every single thing.

00:35:56.901 --> 00:36:00.956
He supplies all your needs.

00:36:00.956 --> 00:36:21.667
Some people need healing or are believing for something that seems impossible—a court order, something with judges or lawyers.

00:36:21.667 --> 00:36:25.800
He's going to come through.

00:36:25.800 --> 00:36:37.053
So we're going to take communion and believe God with you today for your healings.

00:36:37.053 --> 00:36:52.457
We're going to reach out in faith and latch onto the hem of His garment.

00:36:57.159 --> 00:37:03.707
Father, we just thank You, Lord, for healings and manifestations of the glory.

00:37:03.707 --> 00:37:10.320
We believe that Jesus is coming soon.

00:37:16.830 --> 00:37:23.294
I know it in my spirit that we are in the last seconds.

00:37:27.991 --> 00:37:34.108
I believe these are the days of great revival.

00:37:34.108 --> 00:37:57.513
By the stripes of Jesus we're healed and when we lay hands on the sick, they will recover.

00:37:57.513 --> 00:38:07.440
Freely we've been given, freely we give.

00:38:25.140 --> 00:38:41.775
We take this body right now and thank You, Lord, that You were wounded for our transgressions, You were bruised for our iniquities, and with Your stripes we are healed.

00:38:41.775 --> 00:38:55.880
We take the blood and make much of it, for the blood makes much of us.

00:39:02.369 --> 00:39:03.430
We are seated with You far above all principalities and powers.

00:39:03.430 --> 00:39:28.410
A thousand shall fall at our side and ten thousand at our right hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:39:34.213 --> 00:39:35.885
We believe for divine protection and divine provision.

00:39:35.885 --> 00:39:42.826
No weapon formed against you is going to prosper.

00:39:51.244 --> 00:40:02.925
We condemn the words that people speak against us; they will fall to the ground and not bear fruit in our life.

00:40:08.862 --> 00:40:10.169
We believe in the blessing and the covenant.

00:40:10.169 --> 00:40:17.719
We apply the blood over our lives.

00:40:17.719 --> 00:40:26.270
Now, Lord, we lift up Elon Musk.

00:40:26.270 --> 00:40:39.404
I believe that he will be born again in Jesus' name.

00:40:42.311 --> 00:40:44.377
We call him saved.

00:40:44.377 --> 00:40:51.462
Satan, take your hands off of him.

00:40:51.462 --> 00:41:22.440
Lord, You commissioned me to pray for Elon Musk every day for 20 days and I believe he is radically born again, filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:41:27.960 --> 00:41:44.686
I thank You that he will be a loud mouthpiece for Your kingdom, using his celebrity to tell people about Jesus.

00:41:48.846 --> 00:41:51.440
I thank You that his family would know You.

00:41:51.440 --> 00:42:16.960
We call any Jezebel women to be removed in the name of Jesus, not to be a hindrance to his soul being saved.

00:42:18.583 --> 00:42:52.359
We thank You, Lord, that You're putting people across his path to speak life into that man, that he would have a supernatural encounter with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:42:53.569 --> 00:43:08.300
I thank You that he will use the technology for the glory of God.

00:43:08.300 --> 00:43:29.378
Starlink will be used to spread the gospel throughout the whole world.

00:43:31.380 --> 00:43:57.884
We think bigger—that he would be a voice piece bigger than Billy Graham in these last days, a beacon of light shining in the darkness.

00:44:07.629 --> 00:44:22.839
I believe for Hollywood to have a wave of the glory hit the influencers, from the Kardashians to the Kanyes to all of them.

00:44:22.839 --> 00:44:45.940
From Tom Cruise getting out of Scientology to people with huge platforms starting to decree 'Jesus is Lord.

00:44:45.940 --> 00:45:00.343
' I believe for every single person here for everything they need.

00:45:00.343 --> 00:45:08.537
We call them healed and well.

00:45:08.537 --> 00:45:14.743
People are delivered from addictions—fentanyl, heroin, meth.

00:45:21.200 --> 00:45:22.120
We believe today is the day of their deliverance.

00:45:23.653 --> 00:45:28.109
Their marriages are strong and have peace.

00:45:28.109 --> 00:45:40.200
Now, Lord, we lift up President Trump to You for supernatural protection.

00:45:40.200 --> 00:45:45.674
No weapon formed against him will prosper.

00:45:53.310 --> 00:45:53.700
We put angels around him and his family.

00:46:04.893 --> 00:46:05.080
We cover a hedge of protection over our nation.

00:46:05.080 --> 00:46:18.400
I pray a hedge of protection around the people that go to the Thanksgiving Day Parade.

00:46:19.310 --> 00:46:45.234
We take authority over demonic spirits and thank You that all hidden things be revealed to the FBI, Homeland Security, and the CIA.

00:46:45.234 --> 00:46:56.173
No casualties on the Thanksgiving Day Parade or Black Friday shopping.

00:46:56.769 --> 00:47:06.200
We call protection over the malls and New Year's Rockin' Eve.

00:47:06.200 --> 00:47:08.344
No terrorist attacks.

00:47:08.344 --> 00:47:25.500
I've already been praying over Nashville, New Orleans, and Las Vegas for all plans to be revealed.

00:47:25.500 --> 00:47:35.680
Father, I thank You for Israel, that there's peace over Jerusalem.

00:47:35.680 --> 00:47:58.594
And I know what You showed me about them striking oil; I thank You that it will not affect our gas prices.

00:47:58.594 --> 00:48:07.479
We have wisdom and it will not affect us.

00:48:07.479 --> 00:48:15.480
We thank You for creative ideas to get wealth.

00:48:15.480 --> 00:48:24.031
We are blessed in the city and in the field.

00:48:24.031 --> 00:48:29.375
Supernatural provision will come over us.

00:48:29.375 --> 00:48:39.904
Father, I thank You for the avenues You speak to us.

00:48:39.904 --> 00:48:46.394
This is a time to have overflow.

00:48:46.394 --> 00:48:50.200
Do you want to pray?

00:48:50.200 --> 00:49:00.742
I saw someone getting healed of cysts on their ovaries.

00:49:00.742 --> 00:49:06.620
Speak to it right now!

00:49:06.620 --> 00:49:12.329
Cysts, go in Jesus' name!

00:49:12.329 --> 00:49:30.851
